# AI Usage Policy — {{config.siteName}}

**Owner:** {{config.ownerName}} ({{config.contactEmail}})

This policy documents how {{config.siteName}} uses artificial intelligence (AI) systems, what data they process, and the rights users have in connection with those systems. It is written to meet the transparency obligations of EU AI Act **Article 50** and to complement our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service.

---

## 1. When You Are Interacting With AI

Any time you use a feature of {{config.siteName}} that is documented below as AI-powered, you are interacting with an AI system. We will indicate this in-product with a visible label, a system prompt, or an explicit disclosure in the interface. Where AI systems generate text, images, audio, or video shown to you, that output is labelled as AI-generated.

If you are ever uncertain whether a feature uses AI, contact us at [{{config.contactEmail}}](mailto:{{config.contactEmail}}) and we will confirm.

