## 2. AI Systems We Use

The following AI systems are integrated into {{config.siteName}}. This inventory is regenerated automatically on every scan from our codebase.

| Provider | SDK / Integration | Category | Risk Tier | EU Market | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
{{#each systems}}
| {{provider}} | `{{sdk}}` | {{category}} | {{riskTier}}{{#if isOverride}} (declared){{/if}} | {{#if euMarket}}yes{{else}}no{{/if}} | {{purpose}} |
{{/each}}

**Risk tier** follows EU AI Act Article 6 and Annex III:
- **minimal** — limited autonomy, low impact on users
- **limited** — user-facing generation or assistance; transparency obligations apply (this policy is part of that)
- **high** — employment, credit, healthcare, education, biometric, or critical-infrastructure decisions (if any system is classified here, additional obligations under Articles 9–15 apply)
- **prohibited** — social scoring, subliminal manipulation, real-time biometric ID in public (none are ever deployed in production)

