## 3. What Data We Send to AI Systems

When you use an AI-powered feature, the following categories of data may be sent to the listed provider:

{{#if hasInputs}}
- **Prompt input you submit** — text, questions, or requests you type into an AI-powered feature
- **Necessary context** — the minimum additional context (e.g. the page or feature you are using) needed for the model to respond usefully
{{else}}
- **Minimal prompt input** — the specific query or request required by the feature
{{/if}}
- **No persistent identifiers** are sent to AI providers unless you have explicitly signed in and that identifier is required for the feature to work
- **No data from third-party tracking** is sent to AI providers

We do **not** send payment information, passwords, government IDs, health information, or data about other people to AI systems.

